## D3 Reference Implementation

The `D3Adapter` (`src/adapters/D3Adapter.ts`) is a minimal, working reference implementation. It uses the `VIS_D3` node type and demonstrates the full path from descriptor → lifecycle → execution layer → adapter → DOM output, without modifying any pre-existing grammar code.

