## What Was Removed

| Removed | Replaced By |
|---|---|
| `useVegaLifecycle.ts` | `useGrammarLifecycle.ts` + `VegaLiteAdapter.ts` |
| `useUtkLifecycle.ts` | `useGrammarLifecycle.ts` + `UtkAdapter.ts` |
| Per-grammar DOM setup in lifecycle | Moved into each adapter's `render()` |
| Per-grammar GeoJSON preprocessing in UTK hook | Moved into `UtkAdapter.render()` |

